You now have a production-ready Docker Swarm setup with:

✅ **Multiple microservices** (API Gateway, User, Product)  
✅ **Redis caching** for faster responses  
✅ **Redis distributed lock** to prevent race conditions  
✅ **Built-in autoscaling** (no external tools!)  
✅ **Zero-downtime rolling updates**  
✅ **Self-healing** (auto-restart on failure)  
✅ **Health checks** for all services  
✅ **Secrets management** for sensitive data  
✅ **Load balancing** across replicas  

